reviewText: i  never knew this existed i liked it thank you for having it .very good stuff .once again awesome. good

For those of you thinking it's from 1986, it's not. This is actually a heavily abridged form of The NFL TV Follies [VHS] with a preview of Sports Illustrated for the 1987-88 year. Trust me, my dad got this with his subscription of Sports Illustrated a long time ago. It's still funny, but it's not what you think it is.
